      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWRKKTFjDZd/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWRKKTFjDZd/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656339980_18567892561015988_4765528448693268850_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1OTkxMTA0Mzc4NzI3MzgyMTE4NTY3ODkyNTU4MDE1OTg4.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjIzMDR4NDA5Ni5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Q3VoDaHcasQQ7kNvwH2awqv&amp;_nc_oc=AdoYQKBD-AszaCxyCEptnWtdJxG204OG9xW6tjlHzo84ivyuLQ4zvbsV5kkdt5byABo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=LGnX5-sQpo366_EqPBKJKA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy-G_cb44VEpNYxFHIUVYN7979DyuMHI9E2kk3dm8FvPg&amp;oe=69CA0EA7" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @cho_co_pie" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@cho_co_pie</strong></p><p>How I designed a café that does not exist (part 2)<br/>
<br/>
It all started 7 years ago when I was at @artcenteredu . I came across an article about Kopi Joss, a traditional Indonesian drink that mixes charcoal with coffee (I know, kinda odd.) But that article sent me down a rabbit hole of looking for coffee drinks from other cultures that people may have never heard of.<br/>
<br/>
Turns out, there were so many, and each one carried a meaningful history tied to the culture and place it came from. That’s when the idea hit me… What if there was a café that brought all of these drinks together? A place where people could experience a glimpse of the world through a cup of coffee?<br/>
<br/>
After graduating in the midst of COVID, I started working on this every day. The world felt divided and isolating in a way it never had before, and somehow that made this project mean even more to me. And after a few years, I finally finished it.<br/>
<br/>
This was never meant to be a pitch. It was always about telling a story through design, and believing in the power of design to bring people together. <br/>
<br/>
But if this resonates with you, if you love coffee and design, believe in the beauty of diversity, and want to create something together, let’s connect.<br/>
<br/>
Do you think this could be a pop up shop?</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQN32o5HyzF8dODqyeFpPkFnksNNS9euwvB3YZJSP7rBTQRLcvVSMP8ZSfgcYBgYVq6Xr7OSaOQTN6WcvBkOtcLAmu1S0fIyITWFtjE.mp4?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=bnS4z6CtUlYQ7kNvwFhAcOb&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTc5NTQ3OTQ0MjUxMDI0OTksImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjoxLCJ2aV91c2VjYXNlX2lkIjoxMDA5OSwiZHVyYXRpb25fcyI6NTgsInVybGdlbl9zb3VyY2UiOiJ3d3cifQ%3D%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=36c20c95f0dfb532&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=LGnX5-sQpo366_EqPBKJKA&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afzkse6Ioshqxfs8xeYsS7olMIea5SRvY1sWFghT6NQhuw&amp;oe=69C631F0">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWRKKTFjDZd/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
